equestreview-489977322", "createdAt": "2020-09-16T20:00:02Z", "commit": {"oid": "3638a78819a8b8556f2873e8a7c82bfe0b046a05"}, "state": "CHANGES_REQUESTED", "comments": {"totalCount": 1, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyMC0wOS0xNlQyMDowMDowMlrOHTCLTg==", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyMC0wOS0xNlQyMDowMDowMlrOHTCLTg==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDQ4OTcyMDY1NA==", "bodyText": "Suggested change\n        \n          \n    \n\n        \n      \n    \n    \n      \n          \n            \n            When using RestAssured in your test, a connection and response timeout are set to 30s.\n          \n          \n            \n            When using REST Assured in your test, the connection and response timeouts are set to 30 seconds.", "url": "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/12127#discussion_r489720654", "createdAt": "2020-09-16T20:00:02Z", "author": {"login": "gsmet"}, "path": "docs/src/main/asciidoc/getting-started-testing.adoc", "diffHunk": "@@ -159,6 +159,16 @@ quarkus.http.test-ssl-port=8446\n Quarkus also provides RestAssured integration that updates the default port used by RestAssured before the tests are run,\n so no additional configuration should be required.\n \n+=== Controlling HTTP interaction timeout\n+\n+When using RestAssured in your test, a connection and response timeout are set to 30s.", "state": "SUBMITTED", "replyTo": null, "originalCommit": {"oid": "3638a78819a8b8556f2873e8a7c82bfe0b046a05"}, "originalPosition": 6}]}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "1bff3c034067d9421952f29b754b6b30945e1f51", "author": {"user": {"login": "cescoffier", "name": "Clement Escoffier"}}, "url": "https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/commit/1bff3c034067d9421952f29b754b6b30945e1f51", "committedDate": "2020-09-17T08:07:47Z", "message": "Allow configuring the RestAssured timeouts and provide sensible defaults."}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "